pageProduct.name: Wagner Vegan Evening Primrose Oil + Vit D & E 60 Capsules
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Evening Primrose Capsules including Vitamin D and Vitamin E

Warnings

Vitamin supplements should not replace a balanced diet

Common Uses

Evening Primrose Oil with Vitamin D and E is a natural source of Linoleic acid (LA) and gamma-Linolenic acid (GLA) Omega-6 fatty acids with the addition of vitamins D and E.
This formula:
? Maintains female hormonal balance
? Contains Evening Primrose Oil, which supports skin health and maintains skin integrity
? Contains Vitamin D to assist with calcium absorption and Vitamin E an antioxidant
? Created for Vegan and Vegetarians

 

Ingredients

Each capsule provides:
Evening Primrose Oil           500mg
  Equiv Linoleic acid            325mg
Equiv gamma-Linolenic acid  50mg
Colecalciferol (Vitamin D3 300 IU)   7.5micrograms
d-alpha-tocopherol (Vitamin E 22IU)   14.765mg
Encapsulating aids.


 

Directions

Adults Take 1-3 capsules daily with food or as directed by your healthcare professional.
